Coast lobby Haki Africa has taken an anti-corruption campaign &ndash; Red Thursday People&rsquo;s Movement against Corruption &ndash; to Montreal in Canada. Hussein Khalid (pictured) is the lobby&rsquo;s executive director.The campaign seeks to get Kenyans to speak out against corruption. Haki Africa will participate in an international conference whose theme is &ldquo;Unpacking Participatory Democracy&rdquo;.